$y2 = random(-10,-5,1);
$y3 = random(-4,2,1);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
The line through \( ($x1,$y1) \) and \( ($x2,$y2) \) also goes through the point \( (t,$y3) \) for $BR
\( t= \) \{ans_rule(15) \}$BR
EOT
$ans = $x1+($x2-$x1)*($y3-$y1)/($y2-$y1);
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

